 bounce, and within a\nmore realistic model involving matter and $\\Lambda$, is left to future work.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 10 Jan 2022 19:03:55 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 10 Dec 2022 15:38:04 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 12 Jan 2023 11:06:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-01-18"}
