. The attraction between micelles can be well understood in\nterms of DLVO potential. This exothermic adsorption compensates the entropic\ncost, leading to the counter-intuitive behavior of the system.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 10 Jan 2022 20:33:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-01-12"}
