ents\nof the power-law exponents, and yield key insights into the underlying dynamo\nmechanisms that underpin the self-similar flare intensity distributions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 10 Jan 2022 23:43:03 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 5 Mar 2022 16:00:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-04-20"}
